---
title: Extra Cheesy Mexican Beef & Rice Bake with Capsicum & Cheddar Cheese
description: Get ready for a fiesta of flavours with this tonight’s rice bake! Packed with Tex-Mex spiced beef, fluffy rice, and loads of gooey melted cheese, each bite is pure comfort with a spicy kick. Top it off with a dollop of creamy mayo, and you’ve got a crowd-pleasing dish that’s fun, filling, and fabulously flavourful.
